01:02:45,996 --> 01:02:48,896
ふたつ 越えていく夢も
Two, even the dreams we surpass

709
01:02:48,896 --> 01:02:51,696
みっつ つながる絆は
Three, the bonds that connect us

710
01:02:51,696 --> 01:02:54,696
君とひろげてきたんだよ
I've expanded them with you

711
01:02:54,696 --> 01:02:57,396
何度でも咲くように
So that they bloom again and again

712
01:02:57,396 --> 01:03:00,096
続いてくこの物語 "ストーリー"
This story that continues

713
01:03:00,096 --> 01:03:02,896
まだ見たことのない
The scenery I haven't seen yet

714
01:03:02,896 --> 01:03:06,096
景色を探しにゆこう
Let's go find it

715
01:03:06,096 --> 01:03:09,596
花ひとつずつが小さくても
Even if each flower is small

716
01:03:09,596 --> 01:03:11,796
ほら
Look

717
01:03:11,796 --> 01:03:17,396
支え合えたら桜になれるよ
If we support each other, we can become a cherry blossom

718
01:03:17,396 --> 01:03:22,996
ぼくらが繋いだ大きな木は まだ
The big tree we've connected is still...

719
01:03:22,996 --> 01:03:29,896
これからも春風に乗って伸びてくのさ
...going to grow, riding on the spring breeze from now on

720
01:03:39,996 --> 01:03:42,796
ひとつ 涙こぼれたら
One, if tears fall

721
01:03:42,796 --> 01:03:45,696
ふたつ 両手を叩いて
Two, clap both hands

722
01:03:45,696 --> 01:03:48,496
みっつ 数え始めよう
Three, let's start counting

723
01:03:48,496 --> 01:03:51,496
君といれば大丈夫
With you, everything's alright

724
01:03:51,496 --> 01:03:54,296
弱音と本音で泣いたり
Crying with weaknesses and true feelings

725
01:03:54,296 --> 01:03:57,096
諦めかけた分岐 "ルート" も
Even the paths where I almost gave up

726
01:03:57,096 --> 01:03:59,896
振り返って笑うように
So that I can look back and laugh

727
01:03:59,896 --> 01:04:02,796
ずっと強くなれたんだ
I was able to become much stronger

728
01:04:02,796 --> 01:04:06,296
枝ひとつずつじゃくじけそうでも
Even if I'm about to break with just one branch

729
01:04:06,296 --> 01:04:08,496
ほら
Look

730
01:04:08,496 --> 01:04:14,096
支え合えたら大樹になれるよ
If we support each other, we can become a great tree

731
01:04:14,096 --> 01:04:19,796
手と手を合わせた形は花びら
The shape of our hands joined together is a petal

732
01:04:19,796 --> 01:04:26,596
この気持ち言葉すら越えて届けるのさ
I'll deliver this feeling, even beyond words

733
01:04:37,596 --> 01:04:42,696
冴えない私を好きになってくれたこと
The fact that you came to like the uncool me

734
01:04:42,696 --> 01:04:48,296
これからも後悔なんてさせないよ 見ててね
I won't let you regret it from now on either, so watch me

735
01:04:48,296 --> 01:04:51,096
意地を張ってた頃よりも
More than back when I was being stubborn

736
01:04:51,096 --> 01:04:54,096
強く大きくなったでしょう？
I've become stronger and bigger, haven't I?

737
01:04:54,096 --> 01:04:59,596
もっと君を支える側になりたいから
Because I want to be more on the side of supporting you

738
01:05:00,424 --> 01:05:05,744
空に願う星 涙をあずけて
Wishing on a star in the sky, entrusting my tears.

739
01:05:06,224 --> 01:05:11,304
そろそろぼくも 一歩踏みこむよ
It's about time I take a step forward too.

740
01:05:11,864 --> 01:05:17,424
ぼくらが育てた大きな木は ほら
Look, the big tree we grew together...

741
01:05:17,824 --> 01:05:24,584
こんなにも陽だまりのような場所になったよ
Has become such a sun-drenched place.

742
01:05:26,144 --> 01:05:27,984
La La La...

743
01:05:35,064 --> 01:05:36,584
La La La...

744
01:05:38,264 --> 01:05:39,824
La La La...

745
01:05:46,144 --> 01:05:48,584
ねえ 見せてくれたよね
Hey, you showed me, didn't you?

746
01:05:48,584 --> 01:05:51,624
こんなに素敵な未来
Such a wonderful future.

747
01:05:52,104 --> 01:05:54,424
さあ まだまだ続くよ
Now, it's still going to continue.

748
01:05:54,624 --> 01:05:57,944
これからもずっとありがとう
Thank you for everything from now on too.

749
01:06:27,704 --> 01:06:30,944
ねえ 思い出したんだ そっと 涙した日を
Hey, I remembered. The day I quietly cried.

750
01:06:30,944 --> 01:06:34,304
さあ 数えてみようか これまで証した奇跡を
Now, shall we try counting? The miracles we've proven until now.

751
01:06:27,704 --> 01:06:37,104
このあと22時 プレミア公開
Premiere at 22:00 tonight.

752
